## Models

Replace the following files with your trained models
and keep the filenames exactly the same:

### Required files
- CycleGAN weights:
  weights/cyclegan/obesetononobese/latest_net_G_A.pth
- U-Net weights:
  weights/unet/unet_segmentation.pt
- V-Net weights:
  weights/vnet/vnet_segmentation_.pt

### Runtime folders (auto-generated)
Outputs will be written to:
backend/model/runtime/
